      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:47:2",
      "text": [
        " أَنَّهُ نَهَى عَنْ قَذْفِ مَنْ كَانَ عَلَى غَيْرِ الْإِسْلَامِ إِلَّا أَنْ يَكُونَ قَدِ اطَّلَعْتَ عَلَى ذَلِكَ مِنْهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hammad, from Al Halby, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> that he<sup>asws</sup> forbid from slandering one who was upon other than Al-Islam, except that he happened to have been notified upon that, from him’."
        ]
      }
